node.label: Out (Throttle)
node.description: The input signal to be processed.

node.label: In (Starter)
node.description: Works only if anyRPS less than 3

object.script:
function onTick() battery = input.getNumber(1) isCharging = input.getNumber(2)
if isCharging==1 then output.setNumber(2, 0) else output.setNumber(2, 1) end
updIsC = false if isCharging==1 and battery>0.99 then updIsC = true end if isCharging==0 and battery<0.5 then updIsC = true end output.setBool(1, updIsC)
throttleMod = 0 if isCharging==0 then throttleMod = 1 end output.setNumber(1, throttleMod)
end

function onTick() pi2 = math.pi*2 fixedCompass = 180+math.fmod((input.getNumber(1)+1.5)*pi2, pi2)*(180/math.pi) currentCompass = 180+math.fmod((input.getNumber(2)+1.5)*pi2, pi2)*(180/math.pi)
autodir = -1
dif = currentCompass-fixedCompass
if dif>0 and dif<180 then autodir = 1 end if dif<0 and dif<-180 then autodir = 1 end
output.setNumber(1, autodir) output.setNumber(2, currentCompass) end

node.label: In (Current Number)
node.description: The input signal to be processed.

object.script:
function onTick() BaseNumber = input.getNumber(1) ToR = input.getNumber(2) N = input.getNumber(3) answer = false
if ToR==0 and BaseNumber==N then answer = true end if ToR==1 and BaseNumber>N then answer = true end if ToR==-1 and BaseNumber<N then answer = true end
output.setBool(1, answer) end

function onTick() --rear x1 = input.getNumber(1) y1 = input.getNumber(2) --front x2 = input.getNumber(3) y2 = input.getNumber(4) --target x3 = input.getNumber(5) y3 = input.getNumber(6)
distance = math.sqrt(((x3-x2)*(x3-x2))+((y3-y2)*(y3-y2)))
Vx1 = x2-x1 Vy1 = y2-y1 Vx2 = x3-x1 Vy2 = y3-y1
cosO = (Vx1*Vx2+Vy1*Vy2)/(math.sqrt(Vx1*Vx1+Vy1*Vy1)*math.sqrt(Vx2*Vx2+Vy2*Vy2))
sinO = math.sqrt(1-(cosO*cosO))
D = ((x1-x3)*(y2-y1))+((y3-y1)*(x2-x1))
--asin = 0 and +1.6 --acos = 0 and +3.1 angle_to_target = (math.acos(cosO)*180/math.pi)*(-1*D)/math.abs(D)
output.setNumber(1, distance/1000)--meters into kilometers output.setNumber(2, angle_to_target) end

function onTick() FuelKM = input.getNumber(1)
d1 = -1 d2 = -1
if FuelKM > 0 then FuelKM = math.min(FuelKM, 99) d1 = math.floor(FuelKM/10) d2 = math.floor(FuelKM-(d1*10)) end
output.setNumber(1, d1) output.setNumber(2, d2) end

function onTick() Throttle = input.getNumber(1)*100
d1 = -1 d2 = -1
if Throttle < 100 then d1 = math.floor(Throttle/10) d2 = math.floor(Throttle-(d1*10)) end
output.setNumber(1, d1) output.setNumber(2, d2) end

function onTick() curDist = input.getNumber(1) fixDist = input.getNumber(2) update = false
if fixDist==4000 then fixDist = curDist update = true end if fixDist<curDist and curDist<4000 then fixDist = curDist update = true end
output.setNumber(1, math.floor(fixDist)) output.setBool(1, update) end

function onTick() fishIsHere = input.getBool(1) fishDistance = math.sqrt((input.getNumber(2)*input.getNumber(2))+(input.getNumber(3)*input.getNumber(3)))
d1 = -1 d2 = -1
if fishIsHere == true then fishDistance = math.min(fishDistance, 99) d1 = math.floor(fishDistance/10) d2 = math.floor(fishDistance-(d1*10)) end
output.setNumber(2, d1) output.setNumber(3, d2) output.setNumber(10, fishDistance) output.setBool(11, fishIsHere) end
